metadata.name: All eyes on you
metadata.description:
'All Eyes on You', is a mesmerising masterpiece that captures the essence of light and shadow. With its vibrant colours and intricate details, the artwork creates the illusion of perspective colours launching light from three different directions, drawing the viewer's attention towards the subject in the center.

This piece is truly a testament to the power of experimentation and creative expression. Don't miss your chance to own this unique and beautiful artwork.
